{"tid":1605038,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"〈突發〉那位說愛國不等於愛黨的辛灝年為香港作出建議及發聲","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T22:53:24.000Z","uid":286897,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb81eab249cebd3e4fea28c1f0d9d6c8039df37","tid":1605038,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"for those 認識呢個人嘅人可以睇下呢條片先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SSdJlJACKwc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSSdJlJACKwc&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zg2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=7588b826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SSdJlJACKwc</a><br />\n<br />\n前幾日佢開咗個youtube channel叫梅花電視<br />\n用咗個半鐘頭講香港嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AywezvkkJGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAywezvkkJGc&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zg2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=d37af56c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AywezvkkJGc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kjPzht_pgCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkjPzht_pgCQ&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zg2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=0c4d39b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kjPzht_pgCQ</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係總結 你哋都要睇埋條片先好睇 先可能明白我下面講啲咩<br />\n<br />\n 在形式上<span style=\"color: gold;\">突破改良主義( 八九六四民運 )</span>嘅限制， 我們雖然喺內容同埋形式上已經跳咗出嚟啦，但係形式上要更加要跳出嚟。我們唔好「求」中共答應訴求( 64就係衰係求呢樣嘢上面)， 這不是訴求這是「要求」 <span style=\"color: pink;\">佢唔畀都要畀。</span><br />\n  <br />\n2. 今次嘅時代<span style=\"color: gold;\">革命係一個議會革命，民主係一個由下而上嘅體制</span>(香港的例子便是 區議會then立法會)， 佢建議我哋考慮 成立一個  非常時期嘅 Provincal Congress. 作為一個形式上對抗立法會or 區議會嘅機構， 當然呢個對我哋嚟講我為了符合沒有大台的原則，呢個唔會成為大台。 他也用歷史提醒了我們美國獨立革命也是源於英國君主的專制，昔日殘害美國的英國難道不是現在的中共嗎？ 歷史係會重演㗎！<br />\n<br />\n具體來說，辛先生想要的是人民議會的正式籌備公告。<br />\n呢個對中共嚟講會唔會就係<br />\n我哋應該送ge大禮呢？<br />\n又可以將個焦點由警暴shift返去真普選。<br />\n運動可以對焦。<br />\n可能草擬及宣讀有關於臨時立法會\\ 區議會<br />\neg.如果政府選擇暫停區議會選舉則<br />\n <br />\n「香港市民會繼承政府以往舉辨區議會選舉的責任， 市民將會舉辦臨時地區國會議員選舉，以繼續甚至提早順利地選出代表自己區的國會議員，其地位，認受性相等於區議員這一席位。」<br />\n<br />\n打兩面派<br />\n打擊保良派<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能話講就易啫做就難<br />\n但係我哋呢幾個月以嚟<br />\n已經做咗好多好難嘅事㗎喇<br />\n由擔心唔夠人嘅823香港之路， 結果區區都要延長人鏈<br />\n由一首看似平凡嘅我願榮光歸香港，結果成為震驚國際,連結18區市民嘅軍歌<br />\n由畀藍絲挨打，進化成為獅鳥。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你這刻可能感到很灰、很絕望<br />\n但也請你不要忘記<br />\n我們是在種種不可能之中發現出可能。<br />\n我相信辛灝年也把我們這一個特點計算出嚟<br />\n得出了這個結論。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[gold]願榮光歸香港。</span></span>"},{"pid":"cfa1beecf14dd189398d995227aa1873c0709bae","tid":1605038,"uid":3513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"講左好耐但無人識寫憲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108277a74f8a6e64ed7d19c1190d3c841bb85a91","tid":1605038,"uid":317824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"推！乜都試！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de10391f337aaf0c1582f6fe1365d93302f853b0","tid":1605038,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b4b85f2574a4303e1b046d687c21c2fd6004ef","tid":1605038,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"人民議會唔知點解信心唔係好大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a5915937f23037c6116aa2c89a2ea0f611488f","tid":1605038,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://hkrev.info/activity.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Factivity.php&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zg2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=d2