d":"91af5eaee0cdb3bafc2c984615d7d2014a8e8ba4","tid":1605038,"uid":269481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"多謝辛先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗憲法入面其他內容可以參考其他國家憲法然後再研究，最重要嘅係前言，要體現到香港人民意志同立國精神︰<br />\n<br />\n美國憲法前言係︰<br />\nWe the people of the United States, in order to form a more perfect union, establish justice, insure domestic tranquility, provide for the common defense, promote the general welfare, and secure the blessings of liberty to ourselves and our posterity, do ordain and establish this Constitution for the United States of America.<br />\n<br />\n德國基本法前言係︰<br />\nConscious of their responsibility before God and man,<br />\nInspired by the determination to promote world peace as an<br />\nequal partner in a united Europe, the German people, in the<br />\nexercise of their constituent power, have adopted this Basic Law.<br />\nGermans in the L&auml;nder of Baden-W&uuml;rttemberg, Bavaria, Berlin, Brandenburg, Bremen, Hamburg, Hesse, Lower Saxony,<br />\nMecklenburg-Western Pomerania, North Rhine-Westphalia,<br />\nRhineland-Palatinate, Saarland, Saxony, Saxony-Anhalt,<br />\nSchleswig-Holstein and Thuringia have achieved the unity and<br />\nfreedom of Germany in free self-determination. This Basic Law<br />\nthus applies to the entire German people.<br />\n<br />\n睇多幾個國家嘅憲法，應該會有個概念"},{"pid":"cc0b727f4307a77f0a5a4bc9074ea76113b69984","tid":1605038,"uid":169113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"多謝辛先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3210b9edf6ffbb6b1801fd8f9036e55eb66cde07","tid":1605038,"uid":108509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj